{
  "id": "RAW_11c61159",
  "title": "杀入硅谷腹地，MOVA 想在美国庭院发起一场「革命」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&mid=2653097419&idx=1&sn=2536cdf46b3f19802101b3ef9822a202",
  "date": "2026-01-18 07:32:00",
  "author": "极客公园",
  "siteName": "极客公园",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:0em;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;vertical-align:bottom;width:100%;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8cu01Kavc5Yq8Kv8C0BLvGSq6UgVZRHGgRjzE98dT2ZkmjMrNZHgnl2dN1WK6lkxNf8RYNZYa1ic4Zg26WhOZLw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"341\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505613759\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d179f488&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5Yq8Kv8C0BLvGSq6UgVZRHGgRjzE98dT2ZkmjMrNZHgnl2dN1WK6lkxNf8RYNZYa1ic4Zg26WhOZLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:25px 18px 18px;margin:-0.6em 8px 2em;background-size:100%;letter-spacing:0.3px;clear:both;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8em;background-position:100% 100%;background-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hky1mg1\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">MOVA 的目标不只是家电品牌，更要重塑未来的庭院生态。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:25px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz18pn\"><span leaf=\"\">作者｜周永亮</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkziwv\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑｜</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">郑玄</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:48px 8px 25px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1ens\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">CES 2026 的热度刚刚退去，按照惯例，本该进入休整期，去消化那些前沿概念。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzd1r\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">但就在 1 月 16 日，MOVA 却做了一个有些「反常」的决定：他们没有选择休整，而是马不停蹄地在硅谷召开了发布会，正式推出了 M∞VA Universe。这不是单一的产品线，而是一个由 AI 视觉、激光雷达（LiDAR）以及统一智能控制平台串联起来的完整户外生态系统。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1hur\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">最引人注目的，是其产品矩阵中的 LiDAX 和 NAVAX 系列智能割草机器人。MOVA 没有在低价红海中纠缠，而是直接杀入了 2000 到 4000 美元的高端腹地。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzo9\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">选择在硅谷开发布会，本身就是一个巨大的信号。硅谷是全球科技的「精神图腾」，崇尚的是创新、敢冒风险。MOVA 割草机全球营销部 GTM 彭天沁的一番话，更是直接点破了这层深意：MOVA 不想被定义为一家传统的「家电品牌」，而是希望用硬核科技重塑未来的庭院生态。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz17z8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">对于不少人来说，成立于 2024 年的 MOVA 还是个生面孔。但这个新晋玩家的爆发力却不容小觑——2025 年春季产品刚上线核心渠道，仅用半年时间，累计出货量便突破 10 万台，这在同类品牌中是极为少见的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzfg0\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">究竟是什么支撑了 MOVA 如此高速的增长？这家年轻公司进军美国市场的底气，又真正源自何处？</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkja62mvic1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz17bc\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz48c\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">用「激光雷达+全驱」重塑体验</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzmfa\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">美国市场对于任何一家智能割草机器人厂商来说，都是一朵「带刺的玫瑰」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz19f0\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这里占据了全球近六成的割草机市场份额。然而，一个尴尬的数据是，尽管美国人每年在草坪维护上花费很大，但智能割草机器人的渗透率却停留在 10% 以下。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1idy\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">为什么呢？不同于欧洲用户对智能割草机器人有较高的接受度，美国用户要么习惯百元级手推机器的性价比，要么依赖成熟的人工服务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz24mg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这背后主要是因为没能解决核心痛点——效率。美国的庭院环境简直是很多割草机器人的噩梦：平均 1000 到 5000 平方米的超大半开放面积，树木覆盖率高，还有动辄 20° 甚至 30° 的极限坡地。再加上高羊茅、黑麦草这种硬质草类极快的生长速度，传统的割草机器人到了这种环境，要么续航崩盘，要么卡在坡上动弹不得，甚至因为信号遮挡直接变成了「砖头」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzme3\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">MOVA 这次带来的产品矩阵，摆明了就是冲着这些「硬骨头」来的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzdfl\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">从成立之初，MOVA 坚持激光雷达路线。这种执念带来的好处是显而易见的：开箱即用。无需埋设边界线或搭建 RTK 基站，就可以完成厘米级自动建图，具备灵敏避障能力与稳定可靠的运行表现。无论是在树荫、屋檐遮挡，还是强光等复杂光照环境下，设备均能保持精准作业。这种低部署门槛、高环境适应性的使用体验，也是 MOVA 能够在短时间内撕开市场缺口，实现差异化突围的核心逻辑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8cu01Kavc5Yq8Kv8C0BLvGSq6UgVZRHGia0ib1Ep6Oe0icv61kUZoD15PwrNicwfnqrKLoP7wAhLIBlmrAJkeNpSmA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"374\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"374\" data-imgfileid=\"505613764\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8c4245d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5Yq8Kv8C0BLvGSq6UgVZRHGia0ib1Ep6Oe0icv61kUZoD15PwrNicwfnqrKLoP7wAhLIBlmrAJkeNpSmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1gzn\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">此次发布会上，针对超大面积庭院的 NAVAX 5000 AWD 让人印象深刻。它搭载的 Ultra Nav™ 系统，不仅融合了线激光和 AI 双目视觉，更祭出了一项黑科技——「星地一体」无网定位方案。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz6pg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">简单说，「星地一体」就是给割草机的导航上了「双保险」：一条靠地面网络（4G/WiFi），一条靠高精度卫星定位链路。即使地面 4G/WiFi 信号中断，也能通过星基增强服务保持厘米级定位。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1stk\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这套方案本质上是把工业级的技术下放到庭院场景，解决了传统割草机器人「有网是一条龙，断网是一条虫」的尴尬。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz17sb\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">而对于中大面积庭院，MOVA 推出的 LiDAX Ultra AWD，搭载禾赛高精度激光雷达和 AI 双目视觉的融合定位系统。无论是草丛中遗落的玩具，还是突然跑过的宠物，它都能实现对动态障碍物的毫秒级避让。为了应对那些地形更为破碎、复杂的中小庭院，MOVA 还细分出了 LiDAX Ultra AWD Flex，利用单刀盘设计的灵活性，去应对小草坪的复杂地形。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz2ar\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">值得一提的是，这三款新品全系标配了 AWD（四轮驱动）系统。AWD 的加入，利用四个独立驱动电机，让机器在陡坡或湿滑草坪上拥有了强悍的抓地力。配合底部的自适应悬挂系统，机器不仅能爬坡越障，更能在崎岖地形中保持割草高度的一致性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1lnd\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这对于美国用户来说很重要。面对动辄 30° 以上、极具挑战性的坡度，全驱不再是参数表上的炫技，而是机器能否在院子里「生存」下来的基础能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1r8j\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">同时，双刀盘设计与 36V 高压平台的引入，则是为了解决「干得慢」的问题，大幅提升了割草效率。MOVA 这一套组合拳打下来，逻辑非常清晰：他们就是想通过技术突破和对美式庭院的极致适配，撕开美国这个全球最挑剔市场的缺口。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkja6l8k8br\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzsrk\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzwxi\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">从工具到具身智能</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1nis\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">不过，如果你以为 MOVA 满足于止步「家电品牌」的定义，那就太小看他们的野心了。这在子品牌 NexLawn 推出的庭院护理机器人 Master X 上得到了具象化体现。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzsda\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在 CES 现场，Master X 演示的「机械臂捡网球」不仅是一次技术炫技，更向外界传递了一个清晰的逻辑：AI 正在「看懂世界」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6670784434836319\" data-w=\"1619\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"386\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6c230f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5Yq8Kv8C0BLvGSq6UgVZRHGqHlVCm1vtrwf3uibuW6G19WgnPAvKm8P10JibZ6YsXN9dW8vWJnPpOIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzwa4\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这款机器人的硬件架构非常有意思。它是基于 9.8 英寸高的坚固四驱底盘打造，其机械臂在展开状态下延伸至 30 英寸，作业触达高度接近 40 英寸。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzde8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">通过更换多功能夹爪、修剪头与修边刀盘等末端执行器，Master X 突破了传统割草机的能力边界——从清理杂物、精准修边、采摘果实，到协同控制底盘进行精准浇灌，它展示了很高的任务适应性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz19lo\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">虽然这款机器人目前看起来似乎有些「极客」甚至小众，但它代表的是 MOVA 在具身智能方面的思考。除了现在已经应用的星基 RTK 技术，未来他们计划通过大算力 GPU，引入融合大模型的 Agent 软件体系。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzbjz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">庭院环境远比室内复杂，而 MOVA 通过海量数据驱动，构建起硬科技壁垒；团队和数万用户深度连接，持续获取不同庭院场景下的多种障碍物反馈，并完成上万小时的边缘割草与不规则地形训练。这些来自真实世界的反复试错与校正，让机器人不断积累对环境的理解，形成真正属于机器的「肌肉记忆」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1rza\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在 MOVA 的构想中，未来的庭院机器人将拥有机械臂，具备多模态的交互能力。它不应只是一个听令行事的工具，而是具备持续感知、推理、学习和自我优化能力的智能体，真正拥有理解物理世界的能力。「我们希望它能成为一个真正『眼中有活』的管家」，它不仅能割草，还能修剪灌木、识别病虫害进行精准植保；在派对时，它是端茶递水的服务生；在深夜，它是识别入侵者的巡逻员；甚至，它能成为孩子和宠物的玩伴。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1w6u\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">从「自动化工具」走向「具身智能」，机器人正做到理解复杂地形，应对动态环境，未来甚至具备持续学习能力。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkja75ey1ads\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzzmr\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1c6q\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">智能割草机器人站在十字路口</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz4ou\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">回顾科技发展史，我们不难发现，历史总是押韵的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz187u\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果你仔细翻看扫地机器人的进化路线图，会发现今天的智能割草机器人市场，正上演着相似的一幕。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1xol\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">把时钟拨回几年前，扫地机器人也曾经历过很长时期的「人工智障」时期。从最初像没头苍蝇一样的随机碰撞，到后来依靠陀螺仪做简单的弓形规划，直到激光雷达（Lidar）和 vSLAM 视觉算法的真正下放，这个品类才完成了从「玩具」到「工具」的质变。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz115n\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">2016 年是一个转折点，当具备高精度建图能力的产品打破价格与性能的壁垒时，中国市场瞬间被引爆。它证明了只要产品真的好用，用户就会买单。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8cu01Kavc5Yq8Kv8C0BLvGSq6UgVZRHGH0xJCh9t6Q8FicNHwHQb0ic8nOSibngiaEg89mJ4kcZiadYmwI1CVSZjFWg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"375\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"374\" data-imgfileid=\"505613763\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=acdc5302&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5Yq8Kv8C0BLvGSq6UgVZRHGH0xJCh9t6Q8FicNHwHQb0ic8nOSibngiaEg89mJ4kcZiadYmwI1CVSZjFWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1t8j\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如今的智能割草机器人行业，似乎正处于类似的十字路口。虽然目前的市场渗透率还不到 10%，但这背后却积蓄着巨大的势能。在新能源汽车和扫地机器人之后，AI 视觉和激光雷达这些「黑科技」被武装到了庭院场景中。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1me2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">MOVA 选择在硅谷举办这场发布会，意义远不止发布几款新品那么简单。它更像是一个信号，预示智能割草机器人行业「爆发前夜」的到来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkz1dpp\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">美国市场的用户虽然挑剔，但他们的底层逻辑非常务实，那就是对「效率」的极致追求。过去的割草机，要么需要繁琐的埋线，要么避障能力堪忧，要么在复杂地形面前束手无策。而一旦产品解决了连接稳定性、智能避障、以及复杂地形通过性这三大痛点，并且提供极具竞争力的质价比，市场的反馈将是井喷式的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkja9hkzvfg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">对于 MOVA 以及所有在这个赛道上狂奔的玩家来说，游戏才刚刚开始。谁能最先让用户觉得「这玩意儿真省心」，谁就能拿下这个千亿级市场的入场券。而作为那个敢于在硅谷腹地发起冲锋的「破局者」，MOVA 显然已经做好了准备。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "MOVA 通过结合 AI 视觉、激光雷达技术和全驱系统，推出针对美国市场的智能割草机器人，旨在解决传统痛点并重塑未来的庭院生态，从自动化工具迈向具身智能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "MOVA 通过结合 AI 视觉、激光雷达技术和全驱系统，推出针对美国市场的智能割草机器人，旨在解决传统痛点并重塑未来的庭院生态，从自动化工具迈向具身智能。",
